---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import "../styles/sobremi.css";
---

<Base
  title="Sobre mí - Nayara Yap"
  description="Conoce más sobre mi formación, pasiones y experiencia en desarrollo web"
>
  <!-- Hero Section con gradiente animado -->
  <section class="relative pt-32 pb-24 overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Gradiente animado de fondo -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 via-blue-500 to-purple-600 animate-gradient-xy"
    >
    </div>

    <!-- Formas decorativas animadas -->
    <div
      class="absolute top-10 left-10 w-72 h-72 bg-blue-300/20 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-blob"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute top-20 right-10 w-96 h-96 bg-purple-300/20 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-blob animation-delay-2000"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute -bottom-10 left-1/2 w-80 h-80 bg-pink-300/20 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-blob animation-delay-4000"
    >
    </div>

    <!-- Contenido -->
    <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-4 text-center text-white">
      <div class="animate-fade-in-up">
        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-4">Sobre mí</h2>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Conoce más sobre mi formación y pasiones
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Card de Perfil -->
  <section class="container mx-auto px-4 -mt-16 relative z-10 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div
        class="perfil-card bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-2xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-gray-100 animate-fade-in-up backdrop-blur-sm"
      >
        <!-- Foto de perfil -->
        <div class="text-center mb-8">
          <div class="relative inline-block">
            <div
              class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 via-purple-500 to-pink-500 rounded-full blur-xl opacity-50 animate-pulse"
            >
            </div>
            <img
              src="public/img/perfil.jfif"
              alt="Foto de Nayara Yap"
              class="w-48 h-48 md:w-56 md:h-56 rounded-full object-cover border-4 border-white shadow-2xl mx-auto hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
            />
          </div>

          <h3
            class="text-3xl font-bold mt-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
          >
            Nayara Yap
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mt-2">
            Estudiante de Ingeniería de Sistemas e Informática
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Información en cards -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          <!-- Universidad -->
          <div
            class="info-card bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-cyan-50 p-6 rounded-2xl hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
          >
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div
                class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 shadow-lg"
              >
                <!-- icon -->
                <svg
                  class="w-6 h-6 text-white"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5z"></path>
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M12 14l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14z"
                  ></path>
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5zm0 0l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14zm-4 6v-7.5l4-2.222"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Universidad</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-1">
                  Universidad Continental
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Ubicación -->
          <div
            class="info-card bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 p-6 rounded-2xl hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
          >
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div
                class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 shadow-lg"
              >
                <!-- icon -->
                <svg
                  class="w-6 h-6 text-white"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"
                  ></path>
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Ubicación</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-1">Huancayo, Perú</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Correo -->
          <div
            class="info-card bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-emerald-50 p-6 rounded-2xl hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
          >
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div
                class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-emerald-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 shadow-lg"
              >
                <!-- icon -->
                <svg
                  class="w-6 h-6 text-white"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Correo</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-1 break-all">
                  74890597@continental.edu.pe
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Intereses -->
          <div
            class="info-card bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 to-yellow-50 p-6 rounded-2xl hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
          >
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div
                class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 to-yellow-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 shadow-lg"
              >
                <!-- icon -->
                <svg
                  class="w-6 h-6 text-white"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Intereses</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-1">Web, apps, videojuegos</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Badges -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 mb-8">
          <span
            class="px-4 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-red-500 text-white rounded-full shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-300 font-semibold text-sm"
            >HTML</span
          >
          <span
            class="px-4 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 text-white rounded-full shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-300 font-semibold text-sm"
            >CSS</span
          >
          <span
            class="px-4 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-yellow-600 text-white rounded-full shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-300 font-semibold text-sm"
            >JavaScript</span
          >
          <span
            class="px-4 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-800 text-white rounded-full shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-300 font-semibold text-sm"
            >Python</span
          >
          <span
            class="px-4 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-green-700 text-white rounded-full shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-300 font-semibold text-sm"
            >Java</span
          >
          <span
            class="px-4 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-700 to-gray-900 text-white rounded-full shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-300 font-semibold text-sm"
            >Git</span
          >
        </div>

        <!-- Descripción -->
        <div
          class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 via-purple-50 to-pink-50 p-8 rounded-2xl"
        >
          <h4
            class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-center bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
          >
            Mi Historia
          </h4>
          <p
            class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto"
          >
            Soy estudiante del tercer ciclo en la Universidad Continental de
            Huancayo, enfocada en programación, algoritmos, estructuras de datos
            y gestión de bases de datos. Me motiva el aprendizaje constante y la
            exploración de nuevas tecnologías como el desarrollo web,
            aplicaciones móviles y videojuegos. Me considero creativa,
            perseverante y con muchas ganas de seguir creciendo como profesional
            en el mundo tecnológico.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <div class="text-center mt-8">
          <a
            href="/proyectos"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 via-purple-600 to-pink-600 text-white font-bold rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300"
          >
            <span>Ver mis proyectos</span>
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script>
    // Animación de entrada para las info-cards
    const observerOptions = { threshold: 0.3, rootMargin: "0px" };

    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach((entry, index) => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          setTimeout(
            () => entry.target.classList.add("animate-fade-in-up"),
            index * 100
          );
          observer.unobserve(entry.target);
        }
      });
    }, observerOptions);

    document
      .querySelectorAll(".info-card")
      .forEach((card) => observer.observe(card));
  </script>
</Base>
